      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Es tew arri dehſchu / ko\n, tu ne eſſi luḣdsis / ir Baggatibu\nnn Gohdu / ka tahds/ ka tu/ ne\nweens ſtarp teem kehnixeem ne\nbuhs wiſſa tawã Muhſcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un ja tu eeḱsch manneem\nZelteem staigaji/turredams man-\nnus Likkunus/un mannuß Bau-\nſlus/ ittin ka taws Tehws Dah-\nwids irr staigajs/ tad ir es tew\nilgu Dsihwofchanu dohſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un kad Salamans us-\nmohdals/reds/ tad bija tas Sap-\nnis/ tad nahze wiṅsch uhs Jeru-\nsalemi/ un arstahjahs preekich ta\nKUNGA Derribas Schkirſta/\nun uppureja Dedsamo-Uppurus/\nun pataitija Pateitschanaß Up-\npurus / un darrija wiṅeeim fa-\nweem Kalpeeim Dsihres.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. To Brihdi nahze diwi\nMaukas preekich to Kehniau /\nun preſtahjehs preekich winna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Un ta weena Seewa faz-\nzija: Ak! mans Kungs/ es un ſchi\nSeewa dsihwojam weenã Nam-\nmã/ un es eſmu pee winnas tai\nNammmã dsemdejſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Un treschã Deena/ kad es\nbiju dsemdejſti/ dsemdeja ſcht See-\nwa arridsan. Un mehs btjam\nfohpa/ un ne weens Sweſchajs\nbija ar mumã tai Nammmã/ bes\nka mehs diwi ween.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "19. Un ſchihs Seewas Dehls dsihws Behrns peederreja / fa\nNnnn 3\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sirði dewis/ ka tahds/ ka tu ne\nbuhs preckſch tewis bijis / un\npehz tewis arri tahds ka tu ne\nzelſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un ta irr Nakts-Widdũ\nzehluſees/ un irr mannu Dehlu\nno manncem Sahneem ſehmu-\nſi/ kad tawa Kalpone gulleja/ un\nlikke to tawa Klehpi/ un jawu no-\nmirruſchu Dehlu likke ta atkah\nmannã Klehpi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Kad es nu Rihta zehlohs\nfawu Dehlu ſihdiht/ raugi / tad\ntas bija mirris. Bet Rihta es\nwiṅku pareisi apluhkojn/ unreds/\ntas ne bija mans Dehls / ko es\nbtju dsemdejſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tad fazzija ta ohtra See-\nwa: Ne/ bet tas/ kas dsihws/ tas\nirr mans Dehls/ un tas nomirris\nirr taws Dehls. Un ta ohtra at-\nkat fazzija: Ne/ bet tas nomir-\nris irr taws Dehls/ un tas dsihws\nirr mans Dehls/ ta runnajatahs\npreekich ta Kehnia.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Tad fazzija tas Kehniisch\nSchifakka: Tas dsihws irr mane\nDehls/ un tas nomirris irr taws\nDehls. Un ohtra atkat fakka\nTas nomirris irr taws Dehls/ un\ntas dsihws irr mans Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Wehl fazzija tas Keh-\nnisch: Atneffeet man ween\nSobbinu. Un tee atneffe wee\nnu Sobbinu preekich ta kehniaa\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Tad fazzija tas kehniisch\nPahrzehrteet man to dsihw\nBehrnu diwejõs Gabbalõs / n\ndohdeet weenai Gabbalu/ un ot\ntrai Gabbalu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Bet ta Seewa/ kam ta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "irr Nakti nomirris/ tapehz ka\nwinna to irr nogullejſi.\n"
    }
  ],
